Shift Codes
P (Present)
AB (Absent)
UNSCHD (Unscheduled Leave)
NCNS (No Call No Show)
CO (Comp OFF)
WFH (Work from Home)
HALF DAY (Half Day) {Minimum 7 hour login required}
ABSCOND (Absconded Employee)
TERMINATE (Terminated from Services)
RESIGNED (Employee Resigned after serving Notice)
OFF
TRAINING
Calendar Week from Monday to Sunday
Only 2 Off Per Week
Three Consecutive NCNS - 4 day attendance will automatically be ABSCONDED for the remaining of the Month
if any attendance code is marked as ABSCOND/TERMINATE/RESIGNED, remaining attendance for the month will carry forward that code for that employee
Export Options
Only for Admin and Super Admin
Export in .xlsx format
Color Coding for Shift Codes
Add/Edit/Modify Access
Employee Info Add/Edit/Modify - Admin/Super Admin
Attendance Code Add/Edit/Modify - Super Admin
Rest all are view only
Attendance Input
Daily attendance - TL/Admin/Super Admin
Roles assigned will be shared
Employee mapping
HR will share their MIS Excel Sheet with you, you would need to clean and map data as per requirements
